  ('SCIENCE-G4-PSE-SCO67', 'SCIENCE-G4-PSE-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G4-PSE', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G4', '4', 'Processes that Shape the Earth ', 'Assess risks associated with natural earth processes such as hurricanes, floods, tsunamis, and earthquakes.', 3184, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:25.155012+00:00'),
