  ('SCIENCE-G4-PSE-SCO76', 'SCIENCE-G4-PSE-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G4-PSE', 'SCIENCE', 'science', 'G4', '4', 'Processes that Shape the Earth ', 'Identify ways earthquakes impact the environment. (ST 6 LS ECS 16)', 3193, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:25.155012+00:00'),
